WEBVTT

1
00:44:26.830 --> 00:44:28.410 
克瑞娜·史密斯的遗言
The final words of Carina Smyth.

2
00:44:29.250 --> 00:44:30.870 
安静
Quiet!

3
00:44:35.210 --> 00:44:36.670 
克瑞娜·史密斯的遗言
The final words of Carina Smyth.

4
00:44:37.880 --> 00:44:39.970 
尊敬的阁下们 我不是女巫
Good sirs, I'm not a witch...

5
00:44:40.130 --> 00:44:41.760 
但我原谅你们的愚蠢
but I forgive your common dimwittedness

6
00:44:41.880 --> 00:44:43.550 
和空洞的头脑
and feeble brains.

7
00:44:43.720 --> 00:44:45.720 
总之 你们的智商和山羊差不多
In short, most of you have the mind of a goat.

8
00:44:45.890 --> 00:44:47.100 
抱歉 阁下
Pardon me, sir.

9
00:44:47.260 --> 00:44:49.580 
难道临死的人
Is it not common practice for those about to be executed...

10
00:44:49.640 --> 00:44:52.100 
都会被允许 怎么说 发牢骚吗
to be granted a last, I don't know, something...

11
00:44:52.270 --> 00:44:53.540 
要是你耐心点
I believe I was making a point.

12
00:44:53.560 --> 00:44:55.270 
就知道我讲的有道理
If you could just be patient.

13
00:44:55.440 --> 00:44:56.650 
才不
No!

14
00:44:56.820 --> 00:44:59.530 
我的脑袋马上就要落地了 十万火急
My head's about to be lopped off, hence the urgency.

